text.text:
Visited in June2021, with Nexon EV to charge at Statiq 50KW. The location of charger is odd as it has two CCS2 charging guns but very tight space to park two cars side by side as the cables are not long. As the charging place is the only place with shade, normal cars are parked there so need to waste time to ask them to move. The charging screen is difficult to read in daylight. The touch screen is very slow and unresponsive. The help on call was extremely useful and sorted out the issues of unresponsive screen system etc. But lost 30 mins on call and everything before it started charging. At 50KW it is a pretty fast charger. The dhaba is very nice to sit and eat wait while it charges quickly.
Update- used it 3 more times in August2021. Worked without any issues. Fast charge till 95% and then it's slow charging. Need money in Statiq wallet, so top-up at home rather then try it at the location. Airtel signal can be patchy/slow which can cause issues/delays.
